name 'problem-solving-with-ai-preassessment-q13_2025-pilot_v2-2025'

question 'Which of the following best describes why AI-generated content raises ethical concerns about ownership?'

wrong 'AI always creates original work that cannot be traced back to any source.'
right 'AI systems often generate content without revealing or crediting their sources.'
wrong 'AI models are unable to access any human-created content during training.'
wrong 'AI-generated content is always publicly available and free to use.'

allow_multiple_attempts true
